OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mild start to Thursday, with
OL,6,Fcloud and rain moving into the west
OL,7,Fthrough the morning. This clears
OL,8,Feastwards into the afternoon, turning
OL,9,Fcooler behind with blustery showers
OL,10,Fthereafter.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright end to the afternoon
OL,13,Fwith a few isolated showers lingering
OL,14,Finto the evening, however most places
OL,15,Fbecoming dry overnight with cloudier
OL,16,Fskies developing after midnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
